 P.</span> <span property="familyName">Kalva</span>, <span property="honorificSuffix">MD</span></div><div class="content"><div class="affiliations"><div property="affiliation" typeof="Organization"><span property="name">From the Department of Radiology, Massachusetts General Hospital, Boston, Mass. Presented as an education exhibit at the 2007 RSNA Annual Meeting. Received May 6, 2008; revision requested July 15 and received October 23; accepted October 24. S.P.K. received a research grant from AngioDynamics and has been employed by the Speakers Bureau, Johnson &amp; Johnson; T.G.W. is a member of the scientific advisory board of Medtronic; and C.P.C. has no financial relationships to disclose.</span></div></div><div class="core-author-link"><a href="/authored-by/Kalva/Sanjeeva+P" rel="nofollow">View all articles by this author</a></div></div></div></section><section class="core-authors-notes"><h4>Notes</h4><div role="doc-footnote"><b>Address correspondence to</b> C.P.C., Kaiser Permanente, 99 Montecillo Rd, San Rafael, CA 94903 (e-mail: <i><a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#74175a171c151b5a1910341319151d185a171b19"><span class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="7d1e531e151c125310193d1a101c1411531e1210">[email&#160;protected]</span></a></i>).</div></section></section></div><div id="core-collateral-metrics" data-active-pane="false"><header><h2><i class="icon-timeline" aria-hidden="true"></i>Metrics &amp; Citations</h2></header><section id="tab-metrics-inner" role="tabpanel"><h3>Metrics</h3><section>



        
